articles.mainIdea: Palo Alto Networks Stock Is Down But Not Out - Worth Buying PANW Here?
articles.summary: Barchart: Palo Alto Networks Stock Is Down But Not Out - Worth Buying PANW Here?. Palo Alto Networks reported strong free cash flow in Q3, and its FCF margin rose on a trailing 12-month basis. As a result, it could be worth much more, but PANW is well off its highs. That makes it a strong buy for value investors here.
